<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 03:52:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>突如其来的渗透造成超过 250 名以色列人死亡、1,600 人受伤，大规模的炮火震撼了以色列；加沙平民和士兵被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-live/.premium/over-250-israelis-killed-1-590-wounded-civilians-and-soldiers-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018b-0cd2-d8fc-adff-6dfe855e0000</link><description>数十名巴勒斯坦武装分子从加沙经陆海空渗透以色列 ■ 约2,500 枚火箭弹从加沙地带发射 ■ 至少250 名以色列人死亡，约1,600 人受伤 ■ 军队袭击加沙哈马斯目标；据报道，230 名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ “大量”平民和士兵在加沙被扣为人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 03:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-live/.premium/over-250-israelis-killed-1-590-wounded-civilians-and-soldiers-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018b-0cd2-d8fc-adff-6dfe855e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯通过袭击以色列夺取了中东议程的控制权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-seizes-control-of-mideast-agenda-with-israel-attack/0000018b-0b9e-dae9-adcb-abbf9d700000</link><description>哈马斯和巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织现在手中的讨价还价筹码比以往任何时候都强大，他们对以色列和中东其他国家的要求也将如此</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 02:58:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-seizes-control-of-mideast-agenda-with-israel-attack/0000018b-0b9e-dae9-adcb-abbf9d700000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯希望避免巴勒斯坦权力机构注定失败的“现金克制”陷阱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-wanted-to-avoid-cash-for-restraint-trap-that-doomed-pa/0000018b-0bd1-dae9-adcb-abffca0a0000</link><description>该组织长期以来一直在对抵抗的承诺和对加沙超过 200 万居民（包括数万名政府雇员）的义务之间左右为难。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 02:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-wanted-to-avoid-cash-for-restraint-trap-that-doomed-pa/0000018b-0bd1-dae9-adcb-abffca0a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对以色列-加沙战争负有责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/netanyahu-bears-responsibility/0000018b-0b9d-d8fc-adff-6bfd1c880000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 23:24:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/netanyahu-bears-responsibility/0000018b-0b9d-d8fc-adff-6bfd1c880000</guid></item><item><title>像 73 年这样的政治冲击波导致所有系统的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/a-failure-of-all-systems-with-political-shock-waves-like-73/0000018b-0c06-dae3-a1cb-bd0f3be90000</link><description>以色列情报的失败和准备不足并不是唯一的问题——以色列在加沙的作战防御构想似乎已经崩溃。现在，预计以色列国防军将做出大规模反应，不排除在加沙地带采取地面行动以及北部局势升级的可能性。内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯保持沉默，战后将为此付出政治代价</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 23:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/a-failure-of-all-systems-with-political-shock-waves-like-73/0000018b-0c06-dae3-a1cb-bd0f3be90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-加沙战争是 73 年赎罪日的重演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-gaza-war-is-a-repeat-of-yom-kippur-73/0000018b-0b9d-dc5d-a39f-9ffd1d470000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 23:15:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-gaza-war-is-a-repeat-of-yom-kippur-73/0000018b-0b9d-dc5d-a39f-9ffd1d470000</guid></item><item><title>无论本轮以加战争发生什么，我们都已经输了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/whatever-happens-in-this-round-of-the-israel-gaza-war-we-already-lost/0000018b-0b9d-dc5d-a39f-9ffd327c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 23:04:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/whatever-happens-in-this-round-of-the-israel-gaza-war-we-already-lost/0000018b-0b9d-dc5d-a39f-9ffd327c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府应对“23以色列-加沙灾难”负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-government-is-responsible-for-the-23-israel-gaza-debacle/0000018b-0b9d-d8fc-adff-6bfd20090000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 22:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-government-is-responsible-for-the-23-israel-gaza-debacle/0000018b-0b9d-d8fc-adff-6bfd20090000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的鲁莽给以色列带来了战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-recklessness-has-brought-war-upon-israel/0000018b-0b9f-dae9-adcb-abbf348c0000</link><description>哈马斯这个“小”恐怖组织暴露了地区超级大国以色列的赤裸裸。虽然失败首先是军事情报局和辛贝特安全部门的失败，但本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理将无法摆脱这种嘲讽。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 22:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-recklessness-has-brought-war-upon-israel/0000018b-0b9f-dae9-adcb-abbf348c0000</guid></item><item><title>250 名以色列人被哈马斯渗透者杀害； “大量”人被绑架到加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/250-israelis-killed-by-hamas-infiltrators-others-kidnapped-to-gaza/0000018b-0c2a-dae3-a1cb-bd2bb54d0000</link><description>在以色列历史上最致命的袭击之一中，哈马斯利用火箭弹作为掩护，渗透到十多个社区，而政府和军方的反应却十分混乱</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 22:36:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/250-israelis-killed-by-hamas-infiltrators-others-kidnapped-to-gaza/0000018b-0c2a-dae3-a1cb-bd2bb54d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙的空袭造成 230 多名巴勒斯坦人死亡，1,700 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-strikes-in-gaza-kill-over-230-palestinians-and-wound-1-700/0000018b-0bb5-d8fc-adff-6bfdf4ca0000</link><description>阿拉伯媒体报道称住宅楼遭到轰炸，而巴勒斯坦媒体则称死亡人数可能会上升</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 21:38:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-strikes-in-gaza-kill-over-230-palestinians-and-wound-1-700/0000018b-0bb5-d8fc-adff-6bfdf4ca0000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年 10 月 7 日：这个日子将在以色列声名狼藉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/october-7-2023-a-date-that-will-live-in-infamy-in-israel/0000018b-0bbf-dc5d-a39f-9fff47680000</link><description>哈马斯周六的袭击是以色列的一场史诗般的失败，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡领导的国家和以色列国防军在保护其公民方面表现得非常糟糕</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 20:46:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/october-7-2023-a-date-that-will-live-in-infamy-in-israel/0000018b-0bbf-dc5d-a39f-9fff47680000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：美国将确保以色列为其公民提供抵御哈马斯所需的帮助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-u-s-will-make-sure-israel-has-the-help-to-defend-itself-against-hamas/0000018b-0b91-dc5d-a39f-9ff5fe820000</link><description>拜登指出，他从早上 7 点 30 分开始监控这一情况，“哈马斯恐怖分子越境进入以色列，不仅杀害了以色列士兵，还杀害了以色列平民”。在街上和他们的家中，无辜的人被谋杀、受伤，整个家庭被哈马斯扣为人质。这是不合理的&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 19:55:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-u-s-will-make-sure-israel-has-the-help-to-defend-itself-against-hamas/0000018b-0b91-dc5d-a39f-9ff5fe820000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡、拉皮德和甘茨讨论哈马斯冲击渗透期间的紧急联合政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-lapid-says-open-to-unity-govt-with-netanyahu-after-gaza-attacks/0000018b-0b0b-d8fc-adff-6b6f271e0000</link><description>反对派领导人亚伊尔·拉皮德和本尼·甘茨表示愿意加入内塔尼亚胡政府，但拉皮德要求极右翼领导人和部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇和伊塔马尔·本格维尔下台。甘茨同意与两人一起加入</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 17:31:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-lapid-says-open-to-unity-govt-with-netanyahu-after-gaza-attacks/0000018b-0b0b-d8fc-adff-6b6f271e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列户外狂欢大屠杀的幸存者描述“战场”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/survivors-of-massacre-at-israeli-outdoor-rave-describe-battlefield/0000018b-0a85-dae9-adcb-abbfa4990000</link><description>目击者称，数百名与会者遭到来自四面八方的枪击，他们四散躲藏。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 16:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/survivors-of-massacre-at-israeli-outdoor-rave-describe-battlefield/0000018b-0a85-dae9-adcb-abbfa4990000</guid></item><item><title>军方发言人称，“大量”以色列平民和士兵在加沙被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-civilians-and-soldiers-held-hostage-in-gaza-army-spokesperson-says/0000018b-0ac3-dae3-a1cb-bfcb54c90000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人丹尼尔·哈加里表示，周六早上渗透以色列领土的哈马斯武装分子发动暴力袭击，造成平民、士兵和军官死亡。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 16:16:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-civilians-and-soldiers-held-hostage-in-gaza-army-spokesperson-says/0000018b-0ac3-dae3-a1cb-bfcb54c90000</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示美国随时准备在加沙袭击后支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-u-s-stands-ready-to-support-israel-after-gaza-attacks/0000018b-0aca-dc5d-a39f-9eee3c910000</link><description>总统表示，美国警告任何敌视以色列的其他方不要在这种情况下寻求优势。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 15:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-u-s-stands-ready-to-support-israel-after-gaza-attacks/0000018b-0aca-dc5d-a39f-9eee3c910000</guid></item><item><title>目击者讲述加沙渗透到以色列南部后的恐怖事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/eyewitnesses-recount-horrors-following-gazan-infiltration-to-southern-israel/0000018b-0a77-dc5d-a39f-9e77ac2f0000</link><description>周六早上，当哈马斯武装分子袭击基布兹时，加沙边境社区的以色列居民将自己锁在安全的房间里。 “军队需要多长时间才能到达这里？”这是常见的说法</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 14:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/eyewitnesses-recount-horrors-following-gazan-infiltration-to-southern-israel/0000018b-0a77-dc5d-a39f-9e77ac2f0000</guid></item><item><title>“噩梦场景”：哈马斯的胜利是以色列的大规模失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/hamas-victory-is-an-israeli-failure-massive-scale/0000018b-0a1a-d8fc-adff-6b7e7e3b0000</link><description>显然没有关于周六来自加沙地带的震惊袭击的情报，但有初步迹象。现在以色列很可能会以大规模武力回应，不排除进行地面机动并占领加沙地带的可能性。多竞​​技场战役的爆发也是有可能的</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 13:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/hamas-victory-is-an-israeli-failure-massive-scale/0000018b-0a1a-d8fc-adff-6b7e7e3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家安全部长宣布全国进入紧急状态 造成数十人死亡、数百人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-declares-state-of-national-emergency-across-israel-as-22-killed-hundreds-wounded/0000018b-09ba-dae9-adcb-abbf4c0b0000</link><description>大约 2,500 枚火箭从加沙向以色列中部和南部城市发射，最远到达耶路撒冷，而巴勒斯坦恐怖分子则通过陆海空渗透到该国南部社区</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 10:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-07/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-declares-state-of-national-emergency-across-israel-as-22-killed-hundreds-wounded/0000018b-09ba-dae9-adcb-abbf4c0b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>